          Discover fully featured maps from other educators that include standards, objectives, and all the resources you need to teach great lessons.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
    <!-- /Services -->

    <hr/>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="row vspace70">
      <div class="span6 center thumbnail">
        <%= image_tag 'cloud-storage.png' %>
      </div>

      <div class="span5">
        <h2>Google Drive &amp; Dropbox Integration</h2>
        <div>
          <p>TeacherMaps helps you get organized by syncing with the services you already use to store your files.</p>
          <p>Simply select Google Drive or Dropbox, copy your resources to the correct folder, and you’ll be ready to create maps in no time.</p>
          <!-- <a class="btn-theme">Read more</a> -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row vspace30">
      <div class="span5">
        <h2>Standard Aligned</h2>
        <div>
          <p>Standards are the heart of any good unit plan. Fortunately, TeacherMaps already has Common Core standards built in! Simply select your subject and grade level, then choose the appropriate standards from our database. Organizing your curriculum around standards has never been this easy.</p>
          <!-- <a class="btn-theme">Read more</a> -->
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="span6 center thumbnail">
        <%= image_tag 'standards.png' %>
